    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 2,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Per-service resources** \u00b7 pick a service from the **Service** dropdown above. Charts show every pod in that service: CPU, memory, network, restart history. Use this when you have a hot-spot service and need to know which pod is straining."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
